wmimagedock (image slideshow dockapp)

This is a WindowMaker dockapp for displaying multiple images of
various types. Supports png, jpg, gif, xpm using Imlib2. Images
change automatically in order loaded into list or randomly.

Has right and left double click events to execute commands.

Works in WMaker, blackbox, fluxbox, e16.

Replaces wmslideshow or can work in conjunction with it.

There's no man page, but "wmimagedock --help" is, uh, helpful.
